1040
01:19:59,793 --> 01:20:02,130
Feliç aniversari.

1041
01:20:03,489 --> 01:20:06,482
Com ho celebrarem les 3 aquesta nit.

1042
01:20:06,483 --> 01:20:09,529
-Amb molt malbaratament.

1043
01:20:10,938 --> 01:20:14,010
